@danny0405 : Can we please take up flink in another patch. Even for spark, I need to think through quite a bit before we can flip. I created this just to check if all tests pass for now. 
For eg, in case of DefaultHoodieRecordPayload we expect payload props to be set. We do take the preCombine field and set the appropriate payload property. But wanted to follow up compaction, deltastreamer flows to ensure all paths are intact. 
So, even in spark we have some work to be done. would prefer to keep flink in a separate PR.
